      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Error Global Handler\n\n**Purpose:** Centralized error monitoring and logging system that captures workflow failures across all n8n workflows.\n\n**Process:**\n1. **Error Trigger** - Automatically fires when any workflow in the instance fails\n2. **Extract Error Context** - Parses error details including workflow name, execution ID, failed node, error message, and generates execution link\n3. **Send Error Alert** - Posts formatted error notification to Slack channel with all relevant details\n4. **Log Error to Dead Letter Queue** - Persists error record to Supabase workflow_logs table for audit trail and analysis\n\n**Outputs:** Real-time Slack alerts + persistent error logs in database",
        "height": 640,
        "width": 768,
        "color": 6
      },
